title: UPDATE | All lanes open on I-20 EB after multi-vehicle accident
content: AUGUSTA, Ga. (WRDW/WAGT) -- All lanes are now open on I-20 EB near Walton Way Extension after a two vehicle accident.    The off ramp to Walton Way Ext was temporarily shut down, but is also now open..    Richmond County dispatch says they got the call around 2:45 P.M. as an accident with injuries.    No word on the extent of the injuries.    News 12 NBC 26 will keep you updated on this developing story.
